      "pt": "EasyStok segue os princípios da Clean Architecture, garantindo que as regras de negócio fiquem independentes de detalhes de infraestrutura.",
      "en": "EasyStok follows Clean Architecture principles, ensuring that business rules remain independent from infrastructure details."
    },
    "layers": [
      {
